title: BRIEF-Nordic Semiconductor gets $1.9 mln order for components to Consumer Electronics Market
text:
BRIEF-Nordic Semiconductor gets $1.9 mln order for components to Consumer Electronics Market Sept 29 
Sept 29 Nordic Semiconductor ASA : 
* New order for components to Consumer Electronics Market 
* Says delivery of components will take place in Q4 2015 
* Total order value of $1.9 million Source text for Eikon:
